label: 'Perceptions about family planning
definition: Please tell me if you would agree or disagree with the following statements.

label: You could start a conversation with your husband/partner about family planning.
You could convince your husband/partner that you should use an FP method.
You could use an FP method even if your husband/partner doesn't want you to.
You could use an FP method even if none of your friends or neighbors use one.
You could use an FP method even if your religious leader did not think you should use one.
